1
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:37,440
=Have a Crush on You=

2
00:01:38,020 --> 00:01:40,980
=Episode 21=

3
00:01:56,250 --> 00:01:56,960
Liuzheng.

4
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,090
Marry me.

5
00:03:14,610 --> 00:03:18,280
Marry him!

6
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,480
Marry him!

7
00:03:55,810 --> 00:04:00,610
♪It was love that filled this heart
with sweetness♪

8
00:04:00,610 --> 00:04:04,410
♪I'm looking forward to it all the time♪

9
00:04:04,410 --> 00:04:09,120
♪I think of your voice♪

10
00:04:09,170 --> 00:04:11,090
Drink, Ruan Liuzheng! Bottoms up!

11
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:13,720
♪If time could slow down♪

12
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:17,360
♪I never wanted to be apart from you♪

13
00:04:18,410 --> 00:04:19,570
Drink, Ruan Liuzheng!

14
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,200
Dr. Ruan.

15
00:04:22,250 --> 00:04:23,600
Why didn't you tell us earlier

16
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,040
that you are
Deputy Manager Ning's ex-wife?

17
00:04:25,090 --> 00:04:25,730
That's right.

18
00:04:25,730 --> 00:04:27,440
Why didn't you tell us earlier?

19
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,970
Ruan Liuzheng!

20
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:33,290
You've fooled us

21
00:04:33,290 --> 00:04:35,690
about your relationship with Mr. Ning.

22
00:04:35,690 --> 00:04:37,570
The answer to this riddle
is too shocking.

23
00:04:37,570 --> 00:04:38,200
That's right.

24
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,290
I've pursued Mr. Ning

25
00:04:39,290 --> 00:04:41,290
in front of you for so long.

26
00:04:41,290 --> 00:04:43,250
This is so awkward!

27
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,360
You brat.

28
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,880
Are you holding a grudge against me?

29
00:04:47,570 --> 00:04:48,200
How's the result?

30
00:04:48,810 --> 00:04:50,810
Is Set A worth it?

31
00:04:51,010 --> 00:04:52,440
That script is too romantic.

32
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:53,290
So, I edited it myself.

33
00:04:54,250 --> 00:04:54,760
It doesn't matter.

34
00:04:55,090 --> 00:04:56,040
Did Liuzheng say yes?

35
00:04:57,010 --> 00:04:57,730
Yes.

36
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,290
Why are you still unsatisfied then?

37
00:04:59,850 --> 00:05:00,690
I'll make the final payment then.

38
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:01,850
Make the final payment?

39
00:05:01,850 --> 00:05:02,920
Ask him to give me a discount.

40
00:05:03,090 --> 00:05:03,730
Don't make the final payment.

41
00:05:03,730 --> 00:05:05,850
Why are you all alone here?

42
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:06,570
I have to hang up.

43
00:05:06,570 --> 00:05:07,480
Everyone is looking for you.

44
00:05:07,530 --> 00:05:08,290
Come. Let's go.

45
00:05:08,690 --> 00:05:09,010
Let's go.

46
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:09,640
Head Nurse.

47
00:05:10,570 --> 00:05:11,850
Didn't I tell you

48
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,480
to ask Liuzheng to come here alone?

49
00:05:13,810 --> 00:05:14,250
Why did you

50
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:15,570
bring so many people?

51
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:17,850
I'm doing you a favour.

52
00:05:18,130 --> 00:05:19,920
A proposal is something major.

53
00:05:19,970 --> 00:05:22,090
You can't keep it
between just the two of you.

54
00:05:22,290 --> 00:05:24,600
The whole world has to witness it.

55
00:05:25,010 --> 00:05:26,040
Didn't you see

56
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:28,570
how happy Liuzheng is today?

57
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:29,920
Ning.

58
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,640
Well done!

59
00:05:32,010 --> 00:05:33,640
Let's dance. Come on.

60
00:05:55,810 --> 00:05:56,880
The door is opened.

61
00:06:04,530 --> 00:06:05,920
When did you do this?

62
00:06:09,130 --> 00:06:11,320
So pretty. There are even flowers here.

63
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,730
Actually, these are...

64
00:06:18,730 --> 00:06:20,090
I'm so happy.

65
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,640
I never thought

66
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:25,440
that you would say those words.

67
00:06:26,410 --> 00:06:27,440
Today, you said

68
00:06:27,810 --> 00:06:28,730
that when I was gone,

69
00:06:29,130 --> 00:06:31,090
the sky lost its colour.

70
00:06:31,130 --> 00:06:33,530
And that you couldn't let go of me
for the past six years.

71
00:06:34,690 --> 00:06:37,250
Actually, I couldn't let go of you too.

72
00:06:39,010 --> 00:06:40,160
Do you know?

73
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:42,480
For the past six years,
I had regretted it.

74
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:44,760
I really regretted
filing a divorce with you

75
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,290
so recklessly back then.

76
00:06:49,810 --> 00:06:51,040
On the day we were divorced,

77
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,130
when I was packing my bag,

78
00:06:53,570 --> 00:06:56,090
I fantasised about you running to me
to hug me.

79
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,920
I wouldn't leave
if you had hugged me even once.

80
00:07:01,810 --> 00:07:02,810
That day,

81
00:07:04,010 --> 00:07:05,360
I wanted to hug you.

82
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,250
But I didn't have the courage.

83
00:07:08,570 --> 00:07:09,530
I was afraid that you would reject me.

84
00:07:12,010 --> 00:07:14,010
Why would I reject you?

85
00:07:14,730 --> 00:07:16,320
I love you so much.

86
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:19,530
Six years.

87
00:07:19,970 --> 00:07:22,010
Finally, you've come to me.

88
00:07:23,250 --> 00:07:24,290
Finally,

89
00:07:24,690 --> 00:07:26,200
you say that you love me.

90
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,160
Say it again.

91
00:07:37,810 --> 00:07:38,690
I love you.

92
00:07:43,010 --> 00:07:44,320
Say it again.

93
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,320
I love you.

94
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,290
Say it again.

95
00:07:49,290 --> 00:07:51,530
I love you!

96
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,040
So,

97
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,530
after this,

98
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:12,880
can you not lose your temper
with me anymore?

99
00:08:14,130 --> 00:08:14,810
Yes.

100
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:19,290
Can you

101
00:08:19,290 --> 00:08:20,880
humour me after this?

102
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,250
No problem.

103
00:08:23,850 --> 00:08:26,440
Can you give me

104
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:28,920
more surprises after this?

105
00:08:30,810 --> 00:08:32,530
Of course I can.

106
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,120
Do I look pretty today?

107
00:09:17,490 --> 00:09:18,320
Yes.

108
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,730
I think

109
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:22,640
the whole hospital

110
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,370
will be talking

111
00:09:23,370 --> 00:09:24,370
about us by now.

112
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:25,320
They won't.

113
00:09:25,930 --> 00:09:27,090
Of course they will.

114
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,240
Do you want to bet on it?

115
00:09:28,410 --> 00:09:29,200
What are we going to bet on?

116
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,200
Five yuan.

117
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:36,410
See?

118
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:38,680
Nothing is going on.
Everything is as usual.

119
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:49,050
May Dr. Ning and Dr. Ruan
have a lifetime of love

120
00:09:49,050 --> 00:09:51,090
and happiness!

121
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:54,290
Congratulations!

122
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:01,850
Thank you.

123
00:10:02,930 --> 00:10:04,970
Congratulations.

124
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,440
Thank you.

125
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,320
What are you doing?

126
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,240
What time is it now?

127
00:10:13,490 --> 00:10:14,320
It's time to work.

128
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,970
What will other departments think
if they see us like this?

129
00:10:16,970 --> 00:10:17,440
Fortunately,

130
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,530
fate has brought you back to me.

131
00:10:19,530 --> 00:10:21,200
I'll accept your blessings
and congratulations.

132
00:10:21,410 --> 00:10:22,440
But don't do something useless like this

133
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,490
during work hours.

134
00:10:23,730 --> 00:10:25,090
You are my forever.

135
00:10:26,370 --> 00:10:27,410
Please say yes

136
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:28,730
and marry me.

137
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,200
Turn off the computer.

138
00:10:31,530 --> 00:10:32,730
Ask the cleaners to clean this place up.

139
00:10:37,530 --> 00:10:38,290
Hurry up.

140
00:10:38,290 --> 00:10:39,120
Thank you.

141
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,240
Thank you.

142
00:10:44,530 --> 00:10:46,200
Hurry up.

143
00:10:58,730 --> 00:10:59,410
Let's go.

144
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:14,240
Why did you lose your temper
this morning?

145
00:11:14,490 --> 00:11:15,760
They were just trying to be nice.

146
00:11:18,730 --> 00:11:20,760
I'm sure it was planned by Wu Xiaofan.

147
00:11:21,610 --> 00:11:22,640
He's almost 30.

148
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,090
But he still doesn't have
a sense of propriety.

149
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,730
I really think that it was fine.

150
00:11:26,050 --> 00:11:27,120
Don't make a big deal out of it.

151
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,680
They made the office a mess.

152
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:30,490
And with those glitters

153
00:11:30,490 --> 00:11:31,880
all over me.

154
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,240
It was so uncomfortable.

155
00:11:34,410 --> 00:11:36,050
What was it
that you were uncomfortable about?

156
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:46,050
Why do you have to do this?

157
00:11:46,610 --> 00:11:48,320
You must be tired after work.

158
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:50,050
Ning Xiang is not here.

159
00:11:50,610 --> 00:11:51,610
We just need

160
00:11:51,610 --> 00:11:53,000
to eat something simple.

161
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,490
Or we can order food delivery.

162
00:11:54,610 --> 00:11:56,200
That kind of food is oily and salty.

163
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,200
And it's unhealthy

164
00:11:58,090 --> 00:11:59,290
and bad for the stomach.

165
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,320
Here. Give it a taste.

166
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:07,640
I made it with the previous cookbook.

167
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:09,170
I even added some nourishing ingredients
for the stomach.

168
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:10,410
How is it?

169
00:12:15,850 --> 00:12:16,680
Is it good?

170
00:12:21,410 --> 00:12:22,410
To be honest,

171
00:12:22,410 --> 00:12:23,880
you don't have
to go through the trouble.

172
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:24,730
When you were gone,

173
00:12:24,730 --> 00:12:26,120
I ate well too.

174
00:12:36,850 --> 00:12:37,880
The soup is really good.

175
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:39,320
It's warming up my stomach.

176
00:12:41,850 --> 00:12:42,760
Drink more then.

177
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:55,610
When are we going

178
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:56,930
to take our wedding photos?

179
00:12:56,930 --> 00:12:58,880
Now, we need to make reservations
in advance to do that.

180
00:12:59,090 --> 00:13:00,170
When are we going
to take the wedding photos?

181
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:01,930
Do we still need to take wedding photos?

182
00:13:03,170 --> 00:13:04,850
The ones that we took
are quite nice already, right?

183
00:13:04,970 --> 00:13:06,200
The big one that we had
at the head of the bed

184
00:13:06,530 --> 00:13:07,800
is being kept under the bed
all this while.

185
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:08,680
I've kept it well.

186
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:11,090
We can just take it out and hang it up.

187
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,050
And the ring too.

188
00:13:15,370 --> 00:13:16,440
I've kept the ring.

189
00:13:28,170 --> 00:13:29,930
Right? Don't you think
that it's quite troublesome?

190
00:13:30,760 --> 00:13:31,850
Yes, it is.

191
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:32,680
Right?

192
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:33,880
The hospital is so full now.

193
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:35,320
It's better to spend
our free time resting.

194
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:36,530
No need to do those useless things.

195
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,050
Where are you going?

196
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:45,290
Continue with your dinner.

197
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:54,850
If you want to take wedding photos,

198
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:56,760
we can squeeze out some time to do so.

199
00:13:58,490 --> 00:13:59,530
When do you want
to take the wedding photos?

200
00:14:06,370 --> 00:14:08,760
The soup is so delicious today.

201
00:14:34,490 --> 00:14:36,440
Can you stop laughing?

202
00:14:37,090 --> 00:14:38,880
No. Both of you are so funny.

203
00:14:40,170 --> 00:14:40,970
To be honest,

204
00:14:41,610 --> 00:14:44,090
Ning Zhiqian is not wrong too.

205
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:46,410
Are the two of you in the photo

206
00:14:46,410 --> 00:14:47,370
under the bed?

207
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:50,050
Is the ring made to your size?

208
00:14:50,560 --> 00:14:51,530
If the answer is yes,

209
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:53,760
why do you have to waste the money

210
00:14:54,050 --> 00:14:55,200
and time to redo them?

211
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:57,930
But I think

212
00:14:57,930 --> 00:14:58,930
those things

213
00:14:58,930 --> 00:15:00,610
represent a failed marriage.

214
00:15:00,970 --> 00:15:02,880
This time, I want to start anew.

215
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:05,410
It's not like we can't
reuse those things.

216
00:15:05,410 --> 00:15:07,370
And I'm not adamant
that we can't use them.

217
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:09,200
But lately, I really can't accept

218
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:11,090
his attitude towards me.

219
00:15:11,240 --> 00:15:12,800
He's like a totally different person
compared

220
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:13,850
to the one who proposed to me.

221
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:23,410
Deputy Manager Ning.

222
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:25,290
Come. Take a seat over here.

223
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:29,490
You are going to remarry him soon.

224
00:15:29,530 --> 00:15:31,200
You should just be honest with him.

225
00:15:38,170 --> 00:15:39,000
Have you eaten?

226
00:15:39,730 --> 00:15:40,530
I'll eat later.

227
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:51,730
Let me show you this.

228
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:52,760
What is it?

229
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:54,930
This is a shop that's opened

230
00:15:54,930 --> 00:15:55,680
by Xiao'er's friend.

231
00:15:56,170 --> 00:15:57,370
If we want to go there,

232
00:15:57,410 --> 00:15:58,610
they can arrange
the time for us at any time.

233
00:15:58,800 --> 00:15:59,560
Even at midnight.

234
00:16:01,530 --> 00:16:02,760
What about this Saturday?

235
00:16:02,850 --> 00:16:04,680
Do you want to do it
in the afternoon or at night?

236
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:08,290
A Korean-style shop?

237
00:16:09,530 --> 00:16:11,170
You like this kind of style, right?

238
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:14,320
It has been six years.

239
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:15,640
Everyone will change.

240
00:16:17,290 --> 00:16:18,930
What kind of style do you like now?

241
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:20,760
European or Chinese?

242
00:16:24,410 --> 00:16:25,090
What about you?

243
00:16:25,490 --> 00:16:26,530
What kind of style do you like?

244
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:28,730
I don't mind.

245
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:34,560
Yes.

246
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:37,490
That has always been your style.

247
00:16:43,170 --> 00:16:44,880
You are the main character
of the wedding photos.

248
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:46,530
We just need to make sure
that you look nice.

249
00:16:47,560 --> 00:16:48,370
Isn't that right?

250
00:16:54,290 --> 00:16:55,200
We can look at the options.

251
00:16:56,490 --> 00:16:57,970
What about this?

252
00:16:59,410 --> 00:17:00,170
Not this one.

253
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:03,610
This one.

254
00:17:07,970 --> 00:17:09,520
This one looks refreshing.

255
00:17:09,520 --> 00:17:10,250
This looks nice.

256
00:17:10,280 --> 00:17:11,160
We'll choose this one then.

257
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:13,490
It has been so many years.

258
00:17:13,970 --> 00:17:15,250
And you still like
the old-fashioned style.

259
00:17:25,130 --> 00:17:26,010
Didn't you buy any fish?

260
00:17:26,560 --> 00:17:27,250
Here.

261
00:17:28,370 --> 00:17:29,970
I want to eat Chinese sauerkraut fish.

262
00:17:30,770 --> 00:17:31,850
Ask him to make it for you tomorrow.

263
00:17:51,370 --> 00:17:52,490
Hello, Mr. Ning.

264
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,320
Next month, right?

265
00:17:58,970 --> 00:18:01,130
Let me discuss it with Zhiqian then.

266
00:18:04,280 --> 00:18:05,400
Thank you, Mr. Ning.

267
00:18:12,610 --> 00:18:13,850
Let me tell you something.

268
00:18:14,250 --> 00:18:14,850
Go ahead.

269
00:18:15,250 --> 00:18:16,040
Well.

270
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:18,280
We are getting married too suddenly.

271
00:18:18,280 --> 00:18:19,770
So, we couldn't make reservations
for our wedding banquet.

272
00:18:19,770 --> 00:18:21,200
But then,
your father contacted the hotel

273
00:18:21,250 --> 00:18:23,370
where Jiahua held
his engagement party last time.

274
00:18:23,800 --> 00:18:26,090
They say that they have
an empty slot next month.

275
00:18:27,130 --> 00:18:27,970
Sure.

276
00:18:28,090 --> 00:18:29,370
He's quite reliable this time.

277
00:18:32,970 --> 00:18:35,520
Are you okay with the date on the 14th?

278
00:18:35,650 --> 00:18:36,650
I don't mind.

279
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:40,890
It's the 14th of the month.

280
00:18:45,250 --> 00:18:46,040
The 14th of the month.

281
00:18:46,040 --> 00:18:47,610
Foreigners celebrate
Valentine's Day on that day.

282
00:18:47,650 --> 00:18:48,920
And on the 24th, they celebrate

283
00:18:48,970 --> 00:18:50,440
Christmas Eve, right?

