Affiliated Hospital tomorrow morning.

292
00:19:03,370 --> 00:19:04,490
Go to work then.

293
00:19:04,850 --> 00:19:06,130
I'll go with Mr. Ning.

294
00:19:07,770 --> 00:19:10,520
