308
00:19:49,320 --> 00:19:49,770
Not bad.

309
00:19:49,770 --> 00:19:50,560
This is quite good.

310
00:19:51,090 --> 00:19:52,560
That emcee last time

311
00:19:52,560 --> 00:19:53,490
was quite good

312
00:19:53,730 --> 00:19:54,610
at keeping the atmosphere lively.

313
00:19:54,610 --> 00:19:56,650
Fifty tables?
