314
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:57,730
Yes.

315
00:19:57,730 --> 00:19:58,160
Take a look over here.

316
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,090
Look.

317
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:01,130
I've always treated him like my own son.

318
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:03,010
Now, he's getting married.

319
00:20:03,010 --> 00:20:05,770
We should invite all
of Zhiqian classmates, friends,

320
00:20:05,800 --> 00:20:07,130
- colleagues
- Are you satisfied with this?

321
00:20:07,130 --> 00:20:08,520
and all of his relatives

322
00:20:08,770 --> 00:20:09,490
from his family

323
00:20:09,490 --> 00:20:10,040
to attend the wedding.

324
00:20:10,090 --> 00:20:11,970
Let me tell you.
30 tables won't be enough.

325
00:20:11,970 --> 00:20:12,730
Yes.

326
00:20:12,890 --> 00:20:15,010
We should invite
all the relatives and friends

327
00:20:15,040 --> 00:20:16,040
to make it livelier.

328
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:16,490
Yes.

329
00:20:16,490 --> 00:20:17,680
- Isn't it too grand?
- Please wait.

330
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:18,320
I have to take a call.

331
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:19,520
Of course not.

332
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:20,920
This is just nice.

333
00:20:22,650 --> 00:20:23,370
Liuzheng.

334
00:20:23,850 --> 00:20:25,890
Are you satisfied with this venue?

335
00:20:26,010 --> 00:20:27,920
If you like it,
we have to reserve it at once.

336
00:20:28,280 --> 00:20:29,280
It'll be Chinese New Year soon.

337
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:30,010
Many people

338
00:20:30,010 --> 00:20:31,730
will be getting married.

339
00:20:32,010 --> 00:20:33,680
If you hesitate,

340
00:20:34,040 --> 00:20:35,040
we will lose this venue.

341
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:35,850
Okay.

342
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:37,010
Let me call Zhiqian

343
00:20:37,040 --> 00:20:37,970
to discuss with him.

344
00:20:38,770 --> 00:20:39,400
Wait.

345
00:20:39,970 --> 00:20:41,440
There's no need to discuss it with him.

346
00:20:41,520 --> 00:20:43,440
I know my son.

347
00:20:43,650 --> 00:20:45,010
You can just decide on it.

348
00:20:45,650 --> 00:20:46,490
You decide.

349
00:20:47,800 --> 00:20:48,610
That's it then.

350
00:20:49,490 --> 00:20:50,890
I'm sorry.

351
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:52,490
This hall has just been reserved

352
00:20:52,490 --> 00:20:54,040
for the 14th of December.

353
00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:55,650
Our customer has just paid
the deposit for it.

354
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:57,560
I'll pay the deposit now.

355
00:20:57,800 --> 00:20:59,400
Our customer has already paid.

356
00:20:59,520 --> 00:21:01,440
Maybe you can choose another day?

357
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:03,160
Help me check for available dates then.

358
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,250
Please find a hall for us.

359
00:21:04,250 --> 00:21:04,970
Okay.

360
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:10,130
But the holidays and weekends
for the next few months

361
00:21:10,130 --> 00:21:12,160
are almost fully booked too.

362
00:21:12,730 --> 00:21:13,970
We have an available date here.

363
00:21:14,090 --> 00:21:15,040
The 5th of April.

364
00:21:15,490 --> 00:21:17,200
Okay. We'll take it.

365
00:21:17,560 --> 00:21:19,010
The 5th of April.

366
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:20,040
Wait.

367
00:21:22,090 --> 00:21:23,400
That's the Qingming Festival.

368
00:21:23,440 --> 00:21:24,680
How could you suggest it?

369
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:25,730
What kind of a person are you?

370
00:21:25,730 --> 00:21:27,010
Why are you so bad?

371
00:21:27,010 --> 00:21:28,320
Why did you choose that date for us?

372
00:21:28,520 --> 00:21:29,200
How awful.

373
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:29,560
No. You...

374
00:21:29,560 --> 00:21:30,400
I really didn't know.

375
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:31,770
You are too mean.

376
00:21:31,770 --> 00:21:33,090
Did you do it on purpose?

377
00:21:33,090 --> 00:21:34,160
This is your job.

378
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:35,610
How can you not know

379
00:21:35,610 --> 00:21:36,090
what date is it?

380
00:21:36,090 --> 00:21:36,520
Sir.

381
00:21:36,520 --> 00:21:37,010
Ignore him.

382
00:21:37,250 --> 00:21:38,610
He's too mean.

383
00:21:38,610 --> 00:21:40,160
This is not how you do business!

384
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:41,200
I can't believe you.

385
00:21:42,610 --> 00:21:43,400
Madam Liu, are you okay?

386
00:21:43,400 --> 00:21:44,800
Be careful.

387
00:21:44,800 --> 00:21:46,920
You are not young anymore.
If you fall down,

388
00:21:46,970 --> 00:21:47,490
Lean on me.

389
00:21:47,490 --> 00:21:48,250
you'll suffer.

390
00:21:48,970 --> 00:21:50,280
I'm so mad that I'm feeling dizzy.

391
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:52,370
Wait. Let me stand here for a while.

392
00:21:54,280 --> 00:21:55,160
Do you feel better now?

393
00:21:56,560 --> 00:21:57,320
You scared me.

394
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:00,770
Liuzheng.

395
00:22:00,850 --> 00:22:01,800
Don't worry.

396
00:22:02,250 --> 00:22:03,280
I have many friends.

397
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:04,850
I'll ask them

398
00:22:05,090 --> 00:22:06,850
to keep an ear out
for any available slots.

399
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:08,610
We

400
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:11,320
will do our best
to give you a great wedding.

401
00:22:12,970 --> 00:22:14,010
Thank you, Madam Liu.

402
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:16,280
Thank you, Mr. Ning.

403
00:22:16,770 --> 00:22:17,560
Don't worry.

404
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:19,650
Let's go.

405
00:22:19,650 --> 00:22:20,200
Be careful.

406
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:20,650
Are you okay?

407
00:22:20,650 --> 00:22:21,680
I'm fine.

408
00:22:46,010 --> 00:22:46,650
Hello.

409
00:22:47,090 --> 00:22:47,920
Where are you?

410
00:22:48,040 --> 00:22:48,890
Come and pick me up.

411
00:22:49,370 --> 00:22:50,010
Okay. Coming.

412
00:22:57,140 --> 00:22:58,340
(Wanda Realm)

413
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:22,650
Did you manage to book the venue?

414
00:23:23,370 --> 00:23:24,130
No.

415
00:23:24,610 --> 00:23:25,610
What happened?

416
00:23:27,610 --> 00:23:28,250
Let's go home first.

417
00:23:28,560 --> 00:23:29,370
We can talk at home.

418
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:43,920
Your phone is ringing.

419
00:23:44,730 --> 00:23:45,730
You can pick it up.

420
00:23:45,730 --> 00:23:47,250
I think it's from Mr. Ning.

421
00:23:47,250 --> 00:23:48,680
I think he wants to talk
about the wedding banquet.

422
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:51,370
You should pick it up.

423
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,320
I don't want to talk to him.

424
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:01,370
Hello, Mr. Ning.

425
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:04,560
Really?

426
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:07,130
Okay. Send it to my e-mail then.

427
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:08,850
Bye.

428
00:24:10,770 --> 00:24:12,010
Here. Get up for a while.

429
00:24:12,250 --> 00:24:13,040
What is it?

430
00:24:13,610 --> 00:24:15,130
I need to check something.

431
00:24:15,280 --> 00:24:17,090
He has looked up some hotels
that cater to wedding banquets.

432
00:24:17,130 --> 00:24:18,160
He has sent them to my e-mail.

433
00:24:18,490 --> 00:24:20,250
Let's discuss it and give him an answer.

434
00:24:22,490 --> 00:24:23,250
You can make the decision.

435
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:27,520
Go and keep an eye on the fire then.

436
00:24:46,300 --> 00:24:49,340
(Marriage Proposal Package Quotation: A)

437
00:24:58,340 --> 00:24:59,900
(Package B: ￥18500)

