442
00:25:31,620 --> 00:25:35,460
(Request her best friend
to ask her out for a movie.)

443
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:45,800
(Nurse Station)

444
00:25:45,800 --> 00:25:47,320
Hello, Liuzheng. What is it?

445
00:25:49,040 --> 00:25:49,970
I want to ask you.

446
00:25:50,610 --> 00:25:52,650
During the proposal,

447
00:25:52,650 --> 00:25:54,200
did Ning Zhiqian invite Wu and Mei

448
00:25:55,250 --> 00:25:56,520
or were you the one who did it?

449
00:25:58,090 --> 00:25:59,370
I was the one who did it.

450
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:01,130
The more the merrier, right?

451
00:26:01,130 --> 00:26:02,620
(Ask the girl to stay for end credits,
play the proposal video on the screen.)

452
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:04,610
So, Ning Zhiqian

453
00:26:04,610 --> 00:26:06,090
didn't know that they would
be there, right?

454
00:26:06,320 --> 00:26:07,520
Why are you asking me that?

455
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:09,090
Just tell me.

456
00:26:09,320 --> 00:26:10,560
Ning Zhiqian

457
00:26:10,890 --> 00:26:11,730
didn't know about it.

458
00:26:13,610 --> 00:26:14,130
Okay.

459
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:15,250
I got it now.

460
00:26:19,090 --> 00:26:20,320
It's time to work.

461
00:26:20,850 --> 00:26:22,490
What will other departments think
if they see us like this?

462
00:26:23,130 --> 00:26:24,890
I'll accept your blessings
and congratulations.

463
00:26:25,040 --> 00:26:26,090
But don't do something useless like this

464
00:26:26,090 --> 00:26:27,130
during work hours.

465
00:26:30,940 --> 00:26:36,420
(I lost you six years ago. When
you were gone, my sky lost its colour.)

466
00:26:40,180 --> 00:26:45,220
(Package A: ￥39800)

467
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:56,730
I've heated up the soup.

468
00:26:57,280 --> 00:26:59,090
You don't have to cook.
Let's just order in.

469
00:27:00,100 --> 00:27:02,380
(Marriage Proposal Package Quotation: A)

470
00:27:06,770 --> 00:27:08,440
You spent a lot on this.

471
00:27:09,850 --> 00:27:11,090
It's for my future wife.

472
00:27:11,090 --> 00:27:12,010
Of course I have to put in some money.

473
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:13,610
That's quite the effort.

474
00:27:14,280 --> 00:27:16,200
Those candles, balloons
and fresh flowers

475
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:17,610
are prepared by others.

476
00:27:17,730 --> 00:27:19,490
Even the script is written by another.

477
00:27:20,090 --> 00:27:21,490
No. I did change the script.

478
00:27:21,490 --> 00:27:22,400
His script is too cloyingly sweet.

479
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:23,400
I didn't use his script.

480
00:27:24,040 --> 00:27:24,970
If you knew

481
00:27:24,970 --> 00:27:26,520
that so many of your colleagues
would be there,

482
00:27:26,520 --> 00:27:28,250
you wouldn't be able to say
those romantic words, right?

483
00:27:30,040 --> 00:27:31,400
No wonder you were so mad

484
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:32,520
the next day at the office.

485
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:34,850
You felt ashamed for proposing to me.

486
00:27:36,250 --> 00:27:38,250
Nonsense. You think too much.

487
00:27:38,250 --> 00:27:39,400
I did think too much.

488
00:27:40,650 --> 00:27:42,370
I thought that I could change you.

489
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:44,890
You can never change someone.

490
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:47,800
Yes. I admit

491
00:27:47,800 --> 00:27:49,920
that I hired a planning company
to help me.

492
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:51,970
But I'm really sincere towards you.

493
00:27:52,250 --> 00:27:53,440
I spent tens of thousands on it.

494
00:27:53,490 --> 00:27:54,370
Tens of thousands?

495
00:27:54,610 --> 00:27:55,970
Why did you spend so much on it?

496
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:57,800
It cost a few months of your salary.

497
00:27:58,250 --> 00:27:59,490
Isn't that what you want?

498
00:27:59,490 --> 00:28:01,200
What I want is your sincerity.

499
00:28:01,730 --> 00:28:02,920
I don't need a wedding banquet.

500
00:28:02,920 --> 00:28:04,400
I don't even need
to take wedding photos.

501
00:28:04,770 --> 00:28:07,090
But I want to know
if your love for me is true or not.

502
00:28:07,090 --> 00:28:08,280
Of course I love you.

503
00:28:08,320 --> 00:28:09,970
Otherwise, why would I do it?

504
00:28:09,970 --> 00:28:11,130
A romantic surprise.

505
00:28:11,130 --> 00:28:12,010
I gave you everything

506
00:28:12,010 --> 00:28:13,250
that you wanted, right?

507
00:28:13,250 --> 00:28:15,200
You haven't changed at all
even after six years.

508
00:28:15,250 --> 00:28:16,200
Says who?

509
00:28:16,200 --> 00:28:17,490
I've been working on it, right?

510
00:28:18,040 --> 00:28:19,250
Do you really need me?

511
00:28:19,250 --> 00:28:20,280
Of course I need you.

512
00:28:20,320 --> 00:28:21,920
You just need someone to accompany you

513
00:28:21,920 --> 00:28:23,280
and raise your kid together with you.

514
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:25,400
Isn't it good to have a stable life?

515
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:26,370
There's nothing wrong with it.

516
00:28:26,650 --> 00:28:28,130
But it's not something that I want.

517
00:28:28,130 --> 00:28:29,680
No. What do you want then?

518
00:28:30,370 --> 00:28:32,440
I just want an equal relationship.

519
00:28:32,490 --> 00:28:33,560
It was not equal six years ago.

520
00:28:33,560 --> 00:28:34,650
And it's not equal now.

521
00:28:37,010 --> 00:28:37,650
Enough.

522
00:28:37,650 --> 00:28:39,010
Stop mentioning things
from six years ago.

523
00:28:39,040 --> 00:28:39,440
Let go of me.

524
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,520
We'll register our marriage tomorrow.

525
00:28:40,520 --> 00:28:40,850
Let go of me.

526
00:28:40,850 --> 00:28:41,730
Don't be mad.

527
00:28:41,770 --> 00:28:42,650
Don't touch me.

528
00:28:48,250 --> 00:28:49,890
No.
We'll register our marriage tomorrow.

529
00:29:13,580 --> 00:29:19,620
(Huanghai Condominium)

530
00:29:40,980 --> 00:29:45,900
(Beiya Hospital)

531
00:29:57,280 --> 00:29:57,970
It's so late at night.

532
00:29:57,970 --> 00:29:58,920
Why are you here

533
00:29:58,920 --> 00:29:59,920
instead of staying home?

534
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:02,680
You are even drinking.

535
00:30:02,680 --> 00:30:03,970
What happened to you?

536
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:06,770
I feel so annoyed.

537
00:30:07,320 --> 00:30:08,280
Let me drink.

538
00:30:11,090 --> 00:30:12,970
What did Ning Zhiqian do to you?

539
00:30:13,850 --> 00:30:15,560
He wants to register our marriage.

540
00:30:15,680 --> 00:30:16,770
Register your marriage?

541
00:30:17,610 --> 00:30:19,320
Isn't that a good thing?

542
00:30:19,650 --> 00:30:20,800
Do you think

543
00:30:21,370 --> 00:30:22,800
I can have a good married life with him?

544
00:30:23,610 --> 00:30:24,800
Will we divorce again

545
00:30:24,800 --> 00:30:25,920
just like six years ago?

546
00:30:26,280 --> 00:30:26,970
Excuse me.

547
00:30:26,970 --> 00:30:29,160
Why are you asking me that question?

548
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,400
How would I know?

549
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:33,610
But let me be honest.

550
00:30:34,610 --> 00:30:36,890
I don't know if you'll regret

551
00:30:36,890 --> 00:30:38,440
being with him now.

552
00:30:38,850 --> 00:30:40,730
But if you are not with him now,

553
00:30:40,770 --> 00:30:41,850
I know that you'll regret it.

554
00:30:42,090 --> 00:30:44,490
Can you say that you didn't regret it
even once in the past six years?

555
00:30:45,320 --> 00:30:46,800
Why would I regret it?

556
00:30:52,730 --> 00:30:53,440
Sometimes.

557
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:58,160
From what I can see,

558
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,770
you still can't let him go.

559
00:31:01,040 --> 00:31:02,650
Why don't you start a new relationship

560
00:31:02,650 --> 00:31:03,650
with someone else?

561
00:31:04,040 --> 00:31:06,320
You are a firecracker.

562
00:31:06,650 --> 00:31:08,850
You are gentle when it comes to others.

563
00:31:09,040 --> 00:31:11,400
